---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Shorter cadence — notes, updates, and things we built recently for service businesses.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="hero-lite"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="ey">The firm</div>
  <h1 class="h1">Blog</h1>
  <p class="lead">Shorter posts. Things we built, what we're thinking about, and updates from the firm.</p>
</div></section>

<section class="section post-rows"><div class="wrap">

  {% if collections.blog.length > 0 %}
    {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
      <a class="post-row" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <div class="post-row-meta">
          <span class="post-row-date">{{ post.date | date }}</span>
          <span class="post-row-tag">Post</span>
        </div>
        <div class="post-row-body">
          <h2 class="post-row-h">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          <span class="post-row-more">Read &#8594;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
    <p class="muted">Nothing posted yet. The first one is coming.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div></section>

<section class="climax">
  <img class="climax-bg" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dxzw1zwez/image/upload/c_fill,w_2000,q_auto,f_auto/v1779656080/tools_ixpkkk.jpg" alt="Work tools laid out on a surface" loading="lazy" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="se">Next step</div>
    <h2 class="h2">Got a real problem you want a real look at?</h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p>Tell our agent what's going on in your business. We'll dig in &mdash; at no charge &mdash; and find what's actually costing you.</p>
    <a href="/#chat" class="cta">Start the conversation &#8594;</a>
  </div>
</section>
